Title: smart: bring back output as in version 1.6
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1605597600
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b1

In the first innovation release of checkmk 2.0 the output of the smart check plugin
has been reduced, and some of the information was only shown in the servce details.
This is reverted now, and the service output is as verbose as it was in 1.6.
